text: Nazihah Hanis (born 11 April 1997 in Perak) is a Malaysian professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 101 in the world. She has played in the main draw of numerous professional PSA tournaments. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:People from Perak Category:Malaysian people of Malay descent Category:Malaysian female squash players
